Faculty HR Resources
Below are links to the relevant policies, procedures, human resource (HR) forms, and documents related to faculty. Human Resource professionals who are responsible for completing the required campus level approval process will find all necessary paperwork below.  Any questions regarding the information may be directed to facultyaffairs@uic.edu.





